{"tid":939851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加入包圍網！法國最大電信商排除華為5G設備","createTime":"2018-12-13T12:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T00:14:16.000Z","uid":13663,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"72488454dd67e1f686ca6008f4a8eb8a71cd1418","tid":939851,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:28:28.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕越來越多國家、電信商加入封殺中國華為行列，在日本軟銀排除華為，將採用瑞典愛立信及芬蘭Nokia的5G基地台設備後，法國最大電信業者Orange執行長也表示，該公司不會採用華為的5G設備。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》12日報導，法國最大電信業者Orange也加入抵制中國華為設備，Orage執行長St&eacute;phane Richard表示，該公司出於安全考量，沒有計畫在法國未來的5G網路和手機核心設備上，使用華為產品，並較傾向採用愛立信和Nokia設備。<br />\n<br />\n《日經新聞》報導，軟銀已確定，在現存既有的4G通訊方面，將華為等中國製基地台設備，替換成愛立信及Nokia產品，5G設備也將改為採購上述2家北歐公司的產品。"},{"pid":"188427fda12387ba0b1a83476d1d00f10e1ebc2e","tid":939851,"uid":191926,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:31:05.000Z","msg":"太多國家唔用<br />\n<br />\n華為基本已經輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f1f3a2e0122665c99ad2ce9f4e84151787e742","tid":939851,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:34:50.000Z","msg":"可恥"},{"pid":"e9ff5f1d4ac983fbe107f3459eda2bf734d340df","tid":939851,"uid":47492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"188427fda12387ba0b1a83476d1d00f10e1ebc2e","tid":939851,"uid":191926,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:31:05.000Z","msg":"太多國家唔用<br />\n<br />\n華為基本已經輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"強國全部歸邊"},{"pid":"c51e7f708bd8358683d2cee56423b02f22ff4822","tid":939851,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T12:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f04fdbb8e3d7f30eec4a64cb686215587044